2.20	Bulandi_(2000_film)	Bulandi (2000 film)	Bulandi is an Anil Kapoor film, a remake of Nattamai. In Bulundi, Anil Kapor portrays the protagonist, with Rekha and Raveena Tandon in supporting roles. Shakti Kapoor plays the role of the villain. South Indian superstar Rajni Kanth plays the father of the protagonist. Anil Kapoor enacts the role of the head of the village. The story revolves around the environment of a village under the Panchayati Raj rule. The hero's family brings justice to the village.	
